data.description:
This beautiful detached townhome in Brooklyn Park has been extremely well cared for and is truly turn key. The main level boasts an open layout that feels both spacious and cozy. You'll love the eat in
kitchen with new appliances, counters, and backsplash, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The large main level primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and private bath with a separate tub and shower, providing the perfect retreat!

Upstairs you'll find a generously sized second bedroom and a versatile loft that can be used as an office, workout area, or family room. The amazing heated garage is a dream come true, with built-in
cabinets, freshly epoxied floors, and an abundance of upper storage space accessible with a new
lightweight ladder.

The location of this home is truly special, tucked away in its own neighborhood with an abundance of wildlife and easy access to major highways. Just steps to the Coon Rapids Dam as well as miles of walking and biking trails.
